reviewText:
you need a talent!!!! this is a very low qulity movie, but its a movie that had to be made! people want to skip to the part where they are famous and have to answer to no one. you need to do something first.

that is what i got from this movie. its is so bold and in your face that the main lady in the movie has zero skill but wants the fame. what do you do? tell her to go work at Mc Donalds!!!

but she won't listen. why? because she is a FAME WHORE!
